statements: SELECT * FROM dance_competition_results;
SELECT dancer_id, competition_name, score FROM dance_competition_results WHERE final_ranking = 1;
SELECT result_id, dancer_id, competition_name, score FROM dance_competition_results WHERE judge_feedback IS NOT NULL;
SELECT competition_name, score FROM dance_competition_results WHERE score > 90;
SELECT dancer_id, final_ranking FROM dance_competition_results ORDER BY final_ranking DESC;
SELECT * FROM dance_competition_results WHERE competition_name = 'Ballet Competition';
SELECT dancer_id, competition_name, score FROM dance_competition_results ORDER BY final_ranking DESC;
SELECT dancer_id, competition_name, score FROM dance_competition_results WHERE score > 90 AND final_ranking BETWEEN 1 AND 5;
SELECT competition_name, final_ranking, AVG(score) AS average_score FROM dance_competition_results GROUP BY competition_name, final_ranking ORDER BY final_ranking ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT competition_name FROM dance_competition_results WHERE judge_feedback IS NOT NULL ORDER BY competition_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM competition_results;
SELECT id, dancer_name, score FROM competition_results WHERE score > 90;
SELECT dancer_name, feedback FROM competition_results ORDER BY dancer_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM rankings WHERE final_rank < 5 ORDER BY total_score DESC;
SELECT rank, dancer_id, final_rank FROM rankings WHERE final_rank IS NOT NULL;
SELECT id, dancer_name, score, feedback FROM competition_results WHERE score > 90 ORDER BY score DESC;
SELECT dancer_name, feedback FROM competition_results WHERE id = 5;
SELECT id, dancer_name, score, feedback FROM competition_results WHERE dancer_name LIKE '%John%' ORDER BY id;
SELECT rank, dancer_id, final_rank FROM rankings WHERE rank < 3 ORDER BY final_rank ASC;
SELECT dancer_name, IF(score >= 80, 'Qualified', 'Not Qualified') AS qualification_status FROM competition_results;
SELECT * FROM DanceResults WHERE score > 90
SELECT participant_id, score FROM DanceResults WHERE competition_id = 1
SELECT feedback FROM DanceResults WHERE participant_id = 5
SELECT name, specialty FROM Judges
SELECT competition_id, rank FROM Rankings ORDER BY rank DESC
SELECT * FROM DanceResults WHERE competition_id = 1 ORDER BY score DESC;
SELECT participant_id, AVG(score) AS average_score FROM DanceResults GROUP BY participant_id ORDER BY average_score DESC;
SELECT Judges.name, COUNT(Rankings.rank) AS total_ranks FROM Judges JOIN Rankings ON Judges.judge_id = Rankings.participant_id GROUP BY Judges.name ORDER BY total_ranks DESC;
SELECT participant_id, feedback FROM DanceResults WHERE feedback LIKE '%excellent%' ORDER BY participant_id;
SELECT competition_id, participant_id, rank FROM Rankings WHERE rank <= 3 ORDER BY rank, competition_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM dance_competition_results;
SELECT competition_id, dancer_id, score FROM competition_scores WHERE score > 90;
SELECT dancer_id, performance_date FROM dance_competition_results ORDER BY performance_date DESC;
SELECT dancer_id, score FROM competition_scores WHERE judge_id = 1 ORDER BY score DESC;
SELECT * FROM judges_feedback WHERE feedback_text LIKE '%amazing%';
SELECT * FROM dance_competition_results WHERE score > 90 ORDER BY performance_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT dancer_id, AVG(score) AS avg_score FROM dance_competition_results GROUP BY dancer_id HAVING AVG(score) > 80 ORDER BY avg_score DESC;
SELECT dancer_id, overall_rank FROM rankings WHERE overall_rank <= 3 ORDER BY overall_rank ASC;
SELECT competition_id, judge_id, SUM(score) AS total_score FROM competition_scores GROUP BY competition_id, judge_id HAVING SUM(score) > 200 ORDER BY total_score DESC;
SELECT feedback_text FROM judges_feedback WHERE dancer_id = 5 AND judge_id = 3;
SELECT competitor_name, age, gender FROM dance_competitors;
SELECT competitor_name, dance_style FROM dance_competitors WHERE age > 25;
SELECT * FROM competition_scores ORDER BY score DESC;
SELECT judge_name, expertise_area FROM judges;
SELECT competitor_name, position FROM dance_competitors JOIN rankings ON dance_competitors.competitor_id = rankings.competitor_id;
SELECT * FROM dance_competitors WHERE age > 25 ORDER BY competitor_id DESC;
SELECT competitor_name, dance_style FROM dance_competitors WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY competitor_name ASC;
SELECT judge_name, expertise_area FROM judges WHERE expertise_area IS NOT NULL ORDER BY judge_id;
SELECT competitor_name, score FROM dance_competitors JOIN competition_scores ON dance_competitors.competitor_id = competition_scores.competitor_id WHERE score >= 8.0 ORDER BY competitor_name;
SELECT competitor_name, position FROM dance_competitors JOIN rankings ON dance_competitors.competitor_id = rankings.competitor_id WHERE position = 1 ORDER BY competitor_name DESC;
